---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - How I Claude Code" description="Privacy policy for How I Claude Code - we don't track you across sites.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg">
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. We Don't Track You</h2>
        <p>
          How I Claude Code does <strong>not track people across sites</strong>. We do not use third-party analytics pixels, cross-site cookies, or fingerprinting. We respect the <strong>Do Not Track (DNT)</strong> header and skip telemetry entirely when DNT is enabled.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. View Counting</h2>
        <p>
          We count page views using <strong>ephemeral methods</strong>:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>We use a <strong>per-paste 24-hour cookie</strong> to estimate unique views</li>
          <li>We do <strong>not store IP addresses</strong></li>
          <li>We do <strong>not create cross-paste or cross-site identifiers</strong></li>
          <li>We filter out known bots and ignore HEAD requests</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Account Data</h2>
        <p>
          When you create an account, we store:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email address (for authentication)</li>
          <li>API keys you generate (for API access)</li>
          <li>Your conversations (which you control)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not share this data with third parties.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Public Content</h2>
        <p>
          Content you mark as <strong>public</strong> is visible to anyone. Unlisted content is accessible to anyone with the link. Private content is only visible to you.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Aggregate Statistics</h2>
        <p>
          We may publish <strong>aggregate statistics</strong> (e.g., "most popular tags this week") that do not identify individuals. These are derived from public content only.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Data Deletion</h2>
        <p>
          You can delete your account and all associated data at any time. Deleted content is removed from our servers, though cached versions may persist briefly.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about privacy? Contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@howi.cc">privacy@howi.cc</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
